{
  "name": "Morning Vision - Daily Planning",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "path": "vision-daily-planning",
        "responseMode": "responseNode",
        "options": {
          "responseCode": 200
        }
      },
      "id": "webhook-trigger",
      "name": "Webhook",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [250, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {},
      "id": "manual-trigger",
      "name": "Manual",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.manualTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [250, 500]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Provide defaults for manual testing\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    user_id: \"test-user\",\n    session_id: \"test-session\",\n    context: {\n      current_projects: [\"scenario improvements\", \"resource debugging\", \"UI enhancements\"],\n      energy_level: 80,\n      available_hours: 8,\n      mood: \"focused\"\n    },\n    preferences: {\n      focus_areas: [\"deep work\", \"creative tasks\"],\n      avoid: [\"meetings\", \"administrative tasks\"]\n    }\n  }\n}];"
      },
      "id": "provide-defaults",
      "name": "Provide Defaults",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [450, 500]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Merge inputs from webhook and manual trigger\nconst items = $input.all();\nreturn items;"
      },
      "id": "merge-inputs",
      "name": "Merge Inputs",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [650, 400]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Prepare prompt for shared Ollama workflow\nconst input = $json;\n\nconst prompt = `You are a daily planning assistant. Based on this context:\n\nUser Context: ${JSON.stringify(input.context)}\nPreferences: ${JSON.stringify(input.preferences)}\n\nCreate a focused daily plan that includes:\n1. Top 3 priorities for today\n2. Suggested time blocks (morning, afternoon, evening)\n3. Energy management strategy based on current level (${input.context.energy_level}/100)\n4. Potential challenges and how to handle them\n5. Success metrics for end of day\n\nConsider the user's mood (${input.context.mood}) and available hours (${input.context.available_hours}).\n\nFormat as a clear, actionable daily plan.`;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    prompt: prompt,\n    model: \"llama3.2:3b\",\n    type: \"reasoning\",\n    quiet: true,\n    original_input: input\n  }\n}];"
      },
      "id": "prepare-plan-prompt",
      "name": "Prepare Plan Prompt",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [850, 400]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "=http://localhost:{{$env.RESOURCE_N8N_PORT}}/webhook/ollama",
        "sendBody": true,
        "bodyParametersJson": "={{ JSON.stringify($json) }}",
        "options": {
          "timeout": 120000
        }
      },
      "id": "generate-plan",
      "name": "Call Shared Ollama",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.1,
      "position": [1050, 400]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "values": {
          "string": [
            {
              "name": "status",
              "value": "success"
            },
            {
              "name": "message",
              "value": "Daily plan created"
            }
          ],
          "object": [
            {
              "name": "plan",
              "value": "={{ $json }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "prepare-response",
      "name": "Prepare Response",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 3.2,
      "position": [1250, 400]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "respond",
      "name": "Respond",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [1250, 400]
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "webhook-trigger": {
      "main": [[{"node": "merge-inputs", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]
    },
    "manual-trigger": {
      "main": [[{"node": "provide-defaults", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]
    },
    "provide-defaults": {
      "main": [[{"node": "merge-inputs", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]
    },
    "merge-inputs": {
      "main": [[{"node": "prepare-plan-prompt", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]
    },
    "prepare-plan-prompt": {
      "main": [[{"node": "generate-plan", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]
    },
    "generate-plan": {
      "main": [[{"node": "prepare-response", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]
    },
    "prepare-response": {
      "main": [[{"node": "respond", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]
    }
  },
